Maison Souquet is a 20-room hotel inspired by the pleasure houses of the Belle Epoque  . 
  The hotel is situated just steps from the Moulin Rouge and is located in the Pigalle district of Paris . 
  The Celestial Spa boasts a shimmering ceiling of 'stars' and can be rented out for private use . 
  The hotel describes itself as a 'temple to hedonism' and was designed by Jacques Garcia  . 
 